views.markdown: If you need help with "Cream", you can contact CP Digital Darkroom , the developer, via e-mail.
BigBoss  is the maintainer of the package "Cream". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "Gus's Repo" repo, Gus.
